metadata.description: The Hidden 3D Crypto on the Blockchain, the CRYPTOREOGRAM Hidden 3D Coin NFT Collection bring us to a different dimension. Be mesmerize by the 3D coin hidden by your favorite crypto. An art that you can mint, print, and display in your house, office or metaverse. We simply want you to be proud and smile once you see the hidden coin. The question is, 'will you succeed to see the crypto coin?'
